In handwriting analysis ([[graphonomics]]) a '''Movement parameter''' includes [[slant (handwriting)|Slant]], [[Orientation (geometry)|Orientation]], [[Amplitude]], [[Roundness (handwriting)]].


In [[kinesiology]] a '''Movement parameter''' is an adjustable [[scalar (physics)|scalar]] quantity to be specified in a [[motor system]], i.e. movement-control system (See: [[kinesiology]], [[graphonomics]]). Examples are: [[Velocity]], [[Acceleration]], [[Force]], [[Stiffness]].



